headline: Wall Street Analysts Think Constellation Energy Corporation (CEG) Is a Good Investment: Is It?
summary: Based on the average brokerage recommendation (ABR), Constellation Energy Corporation (CEG) should be added to one's portfolio. Wall Street analysts' overly optimistic recommendations cast doubt on the effectiveness of this highly sought-after metric. So, is the stock worth buying?
